<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ScrollView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:background="@drawable/sol"
    tools:context=".Basicpage">

    <LinearLayout
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:orientation="vertical">

        <TextView
            android:id="@+id/textView2"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:fontFamily="@font/days_one"

            android:text="DIET"
            android:textAppearance="@style/TextAppearance.AppCompat.Display1"
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textStyle="bold"
            app:layout_constraintBottom_toTopOf="@+id/foodtitle"
            app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"
            app:layout_constraintHorizontal_bias="0.498"
            app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
            app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf="parent"
            app:layout_constraintVertical_bias="0.719" />


        <TextView
            android:id="@+id/foodtitle"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="71dp"
            android:fontFamily="@font/days_one"
            android:text="Here are 6 science-backed foods and beverages that may provide anxiety relief."
            android:textAppearance="@style/TextAppearance.AppCompat.Medium"
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textStyle="bold"
            app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf="parent"
            app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"
            app:layout_constraintHorizontal_bias="0.313"
            app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
            app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf="parent"
            app:layout_constraintVertical_bias="0.166" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:adjustViewBounds="true"
            android:scaleType="fitStart"
            android:src="@drawable/salmon"></ImageView>

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="156dp"
            android:text="SALMON :- Salmon may be beneficial for reducing anxiety.

It contains nutrients that promote brain health, including vitamin D and the omega-3 fatty acids eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA).

EPA and DHA may help regulate the neurotransmitters dopamine and serotonin, which can have calming and relaxing properties."
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textStyle="bold" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:adjustViewBounds="true"
            android:scaleType="fitStart"
            android:src="@drawable/chamomile"></ImageView>

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="156dp"
            android:text="Chamomile
Chamomile is an herb that may help reduce stress.

It contains high amounts of antioxidants proven to reduce inflammation, which might decrease the risk of anxiety.

Several studies have examined the association between chamomile and anxiety relief."
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textStyle="bold" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:adjustViewBounds="true"
            android:scaleType="fitStart"
            android:src="@drawable/chocolate"></ImageView>

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="156dp"
            android:text="Dark Chocolate
Incorporating some dark chocolate into your diet may also be helpful for easing anxiety,stress.

Dark chocolate contains flavonols, which are antioxidants that may benefit brain function.

They do this by improving blood flow to the brain and promoting its ability to adapt to stressful situations."
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textStyle="bold" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:adjustViewBounds="true"
            android:scaleType="fitStart"
            android:src="@drawable/turmeric"></ImageView>

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="156dp"
            android:text="Turmeric
Turmeric is a spice that contains curcumin, a compound studied for its role in promoting brain health and preventing depression .

Animal and test-tube studies suggest that curcumin may boost the omega-3 fatty acid DHA in the brain by helping your body synthesize it more efficiently."
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textStyle="bold" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:adjustViewBounds="true"
            android:scaleType="fitStart"
            android:src="@drawable/yoghurt"></ImageView>

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="156dp"
            android:text="Yogurt
If you suffer from anxiety, yogurt is a great food to include in your diet.

The probiotics, or healthy bacteria, found in some types of yogurt can improve several aspects of your well-being, including mental health"
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textStyle="bold" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:adjustViewBounds="true"
            android:scaleType="fitStart"
            android:src="@drawable/tea"></ImageView>

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="156dp"
            android:text="Green Tea
Green tea contains L-theanine, an amino acid that has been studied for the positive effects it may have on brain health and anxiety reduction"
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textStyle="bold" />

        <TextView
            android:id="@+id/textView13"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="100dp"
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:text="Â© 2005-2020 Healthline Media a Red Ventures Company. All rights reserved." />
    </LinearLayout>

</ScrollView>